name: Speak With The Jedi Council
Lore: 'Qui-Gon knew that urgency was required. What had transpired on Tatooine demanded the attention of the Council.',
Text: 'USED: If the Jedi Council Chamber is not on table, you may deploy it from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.LOST: Deploy one Jedi Council member to the Jedi Council Chamber from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
